text: Bandu Bhosle (born 10 October 1945) is an Indian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Indian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of India Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
